Subject: [PATCH 2/2] powerpc/p2020: sync the p2020 DTS to FSL NONDPAA SDK 1.0

All these changes are extracted from a bunch of patches
for p2020 DTS in FSL QorIQ NONDPAA SDK 1.0 ISO image.

The highlights include:
- 36bit support.
- ptp timer support.
- l2sram support.
- message interrupt support.
- other minor bug fix.

